#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Create a blog called “Mindful Money\" sharing tips on budgeting, investing, "
"and financial freedom. Use trustworthy colors like dark blue, light gray, "
"and white. Design should be clean and professional with easy navigation and "
"newsletter signup."
msgstr ""
"Erstelle einen Blog mit dem Namen \"Mindful Money\" (Achtsames Geld), in dem "
"du Tipps zu Budgetierung, Investitionen und finanzieller Freiheit gibst. "
"Verwende vertrauenswürdige Farben wie Dunkelblau, Hellgrau und Weiß. Das "
"Design sollte sauber und professionell sein, mit einfacher Navigation und "
"Newsletter-Anmeldung."

#: includes/Admin/AdminTranslations.php:103
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Create a portfolio for a freelance graphic designer \"GrapicVibe\" "
"specializing in branding and visual identity. Use bold, modern colors like "
"black, neon green, and white. Design should be minimal yet striking with "
"large project showcases."
